Chapter 13 

page 324 , after the ssh-keygen command , 
"As a result, my private key (id_rsa) and public key (id_rsa.pub) are copied to the .ssh directory in johndoe’s home directory."
change it to : 
"As a result, my private key (id_rsa) and public key (id_rsa.pub) are copied to the .ssh directory in chris’s home directory."



Chapter 14

page 342  , commenting the output of ip addr show 
"The IP address for localhost is 127.0.0.1/8 (the /8 is CIDR notation, indicating that 127.0 is the network number and 0.1 is the host number)."
correct it with :
"The IP address for localhost is 127.0.0.1/8 (the /8 is CIDR notation, indicating that 127. is the network number and 0.0.1 is the host number)."

